Asia spa
ONE OF THE BEST SPA HOTELS IN SWEDEN
High up underneath the eaves of the hotel, with spectacular views across the sea and small-town picturesqueness of Varberg, you will find Asia Spa. We have created our own little world of well-being and bliss. Allow yourself to be enveloped by warmth and sumptuous scents in a place where it is most definitely allowed to put yourself first.
FIND OUT MORE ABOUT ASIA SPA ›
Vitality pool
A lovely, all-over massage in warm water measuring 30 degrees C. Make your way through the different massage stations and let the jets work their magic on your stiff muscles.
Book a spa package
Read more
Temple room
Our temple room is a sanctuary for the soul. We urge you to take a moment to indulge in quiet contemplation, listen to what your body has to say, breathe and meditate in silence.
Book a spa package
Read more
DARK THERAPY ROOM
