AN OASIS IN THE SOUTH OF SWEDEN - ONLY AN HOUR FROM GOTHENBURG, FIRST-CLASS ACCOMMODATION AND RELAXATION AWAIT YOUR ARRIVAL
Our hotel is located in the centre of Varberg, right at the heart of Halland. Our hotel rooms, where mod cons are combined with charming turn-of-the-century atmosphere, cater to different tastes and requirements. Choose between the three main categories - Classic, Boutique or Deluxe. Perhaps try out a boutique room next time you stay with us and we promise you something out of the ordinary.
Book a room
Classic
Our classic rooms represent a slightly more traditional alternative, boasting a very high standard and comfort. Beautiful wooden flooring and all the latest mod cons.
FIND OUT MORE ABOUT OUR CLASSIC ROOMS ›
Boutique
In our 66 boutique rooms, you will find innovative approaches and unique design features such as round beds or a bespoke bathtub in the middle of the room.
FIND OUT MORE ABOUT OUR BOUTIQUE ROOMS  ›
Deluxe
Our deluxe rooms have been recreated and lovingly restored to their former glory as they would have looked back in 1902. Turn-of-the-century romantic design combined with classic luxury and the latest modern comforts.
FIND OUT MORE ABOUT OUR DELUXE ROOMS ›
Our restaurant
We offer breakfast, lunch, and à la carte seven days a week. In the evening you can choose beautifully created, individual dishes or complete menus from our à la carte menu.
Book a table
Conference in Varberg
Our winning recipe for successful meetings involves equal parts of traditional town-centre hotel steeped in history, modern facilities, a unique Asian spa and fantastic, service-minded personnel ready to go the extra mile.
Send an inquiry
