About us
Contact us
How to find us
A hotel out of the ordinary in Varberg
Dating back to 1902, Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa is one of the most renowned spa and conference facilities in Sweden. We offer top-class accommodation and dining, a place where you can participate at conference in peace and quiet and find true harmony all under one roof.
Contact us
HOW TO FIND US
Our hotel is located in central Varberg, close to both the sea and the train station. Find detailed directions and parking options listed here.
How to find us ›
A UNIQUE HOTEL WITH TURN-OF-THE-CENTURY CHARM
Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa is a hotel that offers you a whole range of amazing experiences and an exceptional Asian spa. We have created a fusion between atmospheric turn-of-the-century ambience and influences from the Far East. Out of a total of 178 hotel rooms, 66 are Boutique rooms with a special flare of individuality both in the furnishings and interior design. All the rooms are non-smoking and we also have 20 conference rooms, an auditory and a magnificent banqueting hall.
Boutique Garden
Boutique Garden
Boutique Prestige
Boutique Romance
Boutique Romance
