Asia Spa – 2 nights
Enjoy spa in Varberg
Three wonderful days and two nights with breakfast, dinner and spa included. Available to book for arrival on any day of your choice.
This package includes:
Two nights in one of our comfortable double rooms (single surcharge applies) and our lavish breakfast buffet.
A delicious three-course meal on your first evening, a sumptuous four-course meal on the second evening and lunch on day 2 as well. All served in our restaurant.
Full access to Asia Spa during your entire stay.
Spa kit with yukata (Japanese bathrobe) and slippers to take home with you as a memento.
Strictly over 15s only (except from during the summer). Children over 15 are booked in as adults.
Read more
