TREATMENTS AVAILABLE AT ASIA SPA
If you want to make your stay with us at Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa extra special and extra relaxing, we recommend you book one of our spa treatments. Why not try a relaxing massage or one of our unique Ayurvedic treatments that will make your spa experience truly extraordinary?
FACIAL, SPA BATH OR THAI MASSAGE  –  GIVE YOURSELF A SPECIAL PAMPERING WITH TREATMENTS  TRADITIONALLY USED FOR THOUSANDS OF YEARS
Many of our spa treatments tie in with Eastern philosophies, such as Ayurveda and The Five Elements, where the focus is to find the right balance and satisfying both the inner and the outer sense of well-being. The fact that these philosophies are tried and tested has been well-documented and for thousands of years, these theories have been the basis for strengthening the human body and readjusting imbalances within. Something we are sure you will feel, and experience the difference afterwards, if you book a treatment at our spa.
Book your spa treatment by email
As our spa treatments are incredibly popular, we recommend you book your session at the same time as you book your chosen spa package to avoid disappointment.
We have a strict over-15s-only rule when it comes to all our spa treatments and facials.
Please use the following email address or phone number to book your spa treatment:
bokning@varbergsstadshotell.com
+46 (0)340-69 01 08
BOOK ONE OF OUR SPA TREATMENTS WITH A CONSULTATION
STRUGGLING TO CHOOSE THE RIGHT SPA TREATMENT?
We completely understand that choosing the right treatment could be tricky, especially if you are buying this experience as a gift for someone else. This is exactly why we have created a range of different packages where we offer a 5-minute consultation with a massage therapist before you take your pick of the available spa treatments below. Our spa treatments with consultation can also be chosen as an additional option when you book your overnight spa package online.
BLISS - serenity
from 545 SEK incl. consultation
A lovely Indian massage with warm essential oils and scents from the Orient works to create true tranquillity within you. You can choose between the following treatments:  ABHYANGA OIL MASSAGE – 25 MIN, INDIAN HEAD MASSAGE – 25 MIN or SHIRO ABHYANGA – 25 MIN.
ZONE – restorative
from 545 SEK incl. consultation
These treatments are based on Eastern philosophy where the focus is pressure, stretching, trigger points and inner flow. You are dressed in a yukata (bathrobe) and resting on a shiatzu mattress during your session. You can choose between the following treatments: WENLEU MASSAGE – 25 MIN, TAIYANG MASSAGE – 25 MIN or GENKI MASSAGE – 25 MIN.
NAMASTE – oneness
from 745 SEK incl. consultation
Lie back on the massage table, relax and experience oneness with the warm, beautifully fragranced oils, body butter or face care products that all originate from India. You can choose between the following treatments: AROMA MASSAGE – 50 MIN, ABHYANGA LUXURY – 50 MIN or SIGNUM ASIA – 50 MIN.
Book your spa treatment by email
SPA TREATMENTS SPECIALLY TAILORED TO SUIT YOU
AYURVEDIC TREATMENTS
Many of our treatments are based on the Ayurvedic perspective that originates from India. In the theory of Ayurveda, they have divided mankind into three different categories or 'mind-body-types', so-called doshas; VATA, PITTA and KAPHA. Using this knowledge as a starting point, the therapist will analyse your skin and adjust your treatment accordingly.
Abhyanga oil massage – 25 min
Upper body massage with warm, aromatic oils where we focus on head, neck, shoulders, chest and torso. Abhyanga is a Sanskrit term for oil massage.
Suitable for pregnant ladies too.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Abhyanga luxury – 50 min
This particular treatment starts with cleansing, tonic and face masque. While the masque works its magic, you get to enjoy a calming massage on your shoulders, chest and torso. The therapist then finishes your session with a relaxing face massage.
Suitable for pregnant ladies too.
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Aroma massage – 50 min
A glorious full body massage, including face, with warm, delicately fragranced aromatic oils.
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Indian Head massage – 25 min
When you need to still your mind, calm your thoughts and unwind, an Indian head massage will re-energise your whole being. During this session, your head, neck and upper back will be massaged.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Shiroabhyanga – 25 min
A dreamy massage that focuses on the back of your body using warm, aromatic oils. The therapist will work on the head, neck, back and also a few strokes on the back of your legs. Shiro is Sanskrit for head.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Shirodara – a royal treatment – 60 min
The treatment starts with a lovely upper body massage that focuses on your shoulders, chest and torso. The final touch is a calming, warm flow of oil that is poured onto your forehead and head in slow, sweeping movements, which in turn instil a deeply relaxed sensation in both body and mind.
Shirodhara soothes the nervous system and counteracts anxiety and sleep disorders. You also get to keep the oil that has been used during your treatment, so that you can carry on using it for oil massage in the comfort of your own home.
Price:
995 SEK
Signum Asia – 50 min
This is a wonderful full body massage (face not including) using delicately fragranced massage butter that balances your body's doshas; Vata, Pitta, Kapha.
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Stone Swedana – 60 min
You are treated to a heavenly full body massage, where the therapist uses wonderfully smooth stones for extra restorative benefits. At the same time, your body gets to rest on the same kind of smooth stones, which will invigorate you and give you new energy. A magical experience that will stay in your memory for a long time.
Price:
895 SEK
Please use the following email address or phone number to book your spa treatment:
bokning@varbergsstadshotell.com
+46 (0)340-69 01 08
Book your spa treatment by email
REBALANCING YOUR BODY'S ENERGIES
OTHER SPA TREATMENTS
We also offer other body treatments based on Eastern philosophy." In these we use pressure and stretches and our focus is to stimulate the body's various trigger points, circulation and inner flows.
Taiyang massage – 25/50 min
Our unique Thai massage is influenced by different methods and the overall focus is breathing, pressure and stretching. You get to lie down dressed in a yukata (Japanese bathrobe) on a large, comfortable shiatzu mattress, while our massage therapist gets to work on your muscles and joints. Oil massage is included on your legs and arms.
Price, upper body 25 min:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Price, full body 50 min:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Wenleu/Genki – 50 min
If you are struggling to choose between a facial and a foot massage, we have the perfect tailor-made solution for you. You get to lie down dressed in a yukata (Japanese bathrobe) on a big, comfortable shiatzu mattress. We start with your face, you will be given acupressure, lymph drainage and massage to stimulate the warm flows in your face, neck and scalp.
After this, the therapist moves onto massaging your hands and feet with a delicately fragranced, rehydrating cream. The massage will rebalance your body's energy flows.
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Wenleu massage – 25 min
A truly re-energising, invigorating face massage. With the help of acupressure, lymph drainage and massage, the therapist aim to stimulate the warm flows inside your face, neck and scalp. Wenleu means warm flows. Also suitable for pregnant ladies.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Genki massage – 25 min
A truly energising, revitalising hand massage followed by a foot massage to rebalance your body's energy channels and flow. You get to lie down dressed in a yukata (Japanese bathrobe) on a big, comfortable shiatzu mattress.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
