HEAVENLY CLEANSING
WRAPS & EXFOLIATION SCRUBS
Is your body in need of a little TLC? Why not choose a wrap, masque or scrub to both relax your mind for a few moments and cleanse your skin at the same time?
Detox Spa Ritual – 90 min
This spa treatment starts with an exfoliating body scrub, after which the therapist wraps your body in a top-to-toe cleansing algae and clay masque. Whilst your body is cocooned in this masque, you will be treated to a divine face massage and once the masque has worked its magic, you will slip into a warm, detoxing spa tub.
The session ends with a front of body massage with delicately fragranced, warm oil. You will also be served a wholesome detox drink, which gives the benefits of this spa treatment even more depth. The detox drink is also available for purchase in our spa shop, so you can carry on your spa experience in the comfort of your own home.
Price:
1,195 SEK
Lotus Body Scrub – 25 min
This highly effective and calming body scrub with lotus and bamboo extract cleanses, removes old skin cells and stimulates the blood circulation. The result is incredibly supple skin, smooth as velvet and with a radiant glow. Also suitable for pregnant ladies.
Price:
495 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
545 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
