TREAT YOUR SKIN TO A LITTLE TLC
FACIALS
We use two different skincare brands for our facials. The facials with Phyto 5 are based on the Chinese theory of The Five Elements. Eminence Organics is a highly professional, organic and result-driven company. Our facials are however available to everyone, not just spa guests, and can be booked online via email.
Eminence Eco Facial – 50 min
A luxurious facial with anti-age effects and organic products from Eminence. We tailor the treatment to suit your skin.
This is suitable for everyone, even mums-to-be.
The treatment involves:
Double cleansing (no deep pore cleansing)
Peeling
Scalp massage
Face, decolletage, neck and shoulder massage
Face masque
Finishing touches with Eminence products
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Phyto Asia – 50 min
This is a calming, pleasant facial that with the help of lymph drainage removes waste products and excess water from your skin. Your skin will be beautifully rebalanced with products from Phyto 5.
Suitable to all ages and skin types, even sensitive skin.
This session includes:
Skin analysis in accordance with The Five Elements
Cleansing (extraction not included)
Exfoliation
Lymph drainage with coloured light
Face, decolletage, neck and shoulder massage
Clay masque
Price:
695 SEK, Monday - Friday noon
745 SEK, Friday from 2 pm - Sunday, and all Bank Holidays
Colour lift – 90 min
A revolutionary treatment that will give you a natural face lift without any surgical interventions. Advanced technology coupled with ancient Chinese medicine and colour therapy helps to counteract the ageing of the skin, improve elasticity, reduce wrinkles, swelling and dark circles around the eyes.
This session includes:
Cleansing (extraction not included)
Exfoliation
Algae masque
Longer spells of lymph drainage with coloured light, eye area included
Face, decolletage, neck and shoulder massage
Clay masque as well as finishing touches/products
Price:
1,095 SEK
The five elements – 70 min
A classic, deep-cleansing facial that rebalances your skin with products from Phytobiodermie. During this session, the therapist will also balance your chakras with the help of coloured light.
This session includes:
Cleansing
Exfoliation
Algae masque
Extraction (blackhead/whitehead)
Lymph drainage with coloured light
Face, decolletage, neck and shoulder massage
Clay masque as well as finishing touches/products
Price:
995 SEK
Eyebrow shaping – 15 min
Let us take care of your eyebrows for you and shape them to help you achieve your desired look.
Price:
225 SEK
