”Best Spa in Sweden so far and good value”
Paul T
TRIPADVISOR
CHOOSE ONE OF OUR SPA TREATMENTS OR TAKE A PEW IN ONE OF OUR POOLS OVERLOOKING VARBERG
With the help of warm pools, wholesome spa treatments and unique, Asian-inspired surroundings, we have created a space where the hustle and bustle of everyday life fades away into a distant memory. Step into tranquillity and immerse yourself in soothing warmth and heavenly aromas. At Asia Spa, the calm, unhurried pace and hushed conversations add to the restful ambience.
OUR RANGE OF SPA TREATMENTS
A unique spa promising something out of the ordinary
Calm, unhurried movements and hushed voices help to maintain the tranquil atmosphere at Asia Spa. Over 15s only are admitted, apart from a few weeks in the middle of the summer when we allow younger children to experience the spa.
Ablution
Start your spa experience with a Japanese ablution ritual. Scrubbing oneself is seen as a ritual where both body and soul should be cleansed. Take a seat on a wooden stool in one of our ablution rooms and allow the warm, gentle water to wash over you. Give yourself time to reflect and ponder.
NEW ADDITION AT ASIA SPA
Surya & Orangery
At long last, we are ready to welcome you as our guests to a new area for rest and recuperation at Asia Spa. On the top floor, close to the Vitality pool, you can now access our new orangery and the Surya relaxation lounge.
Read more about our new addition ›
Pool & Sauna oasis
Slip down into the warm water in our hot springs, explore several different kinds of saunas and enjoy a lovely all-over massage in our Vitality pool.
Read more about Pool & Sauna ›
Peacock House
Peacock House is our tranquillity therapy section, where you will find different rooms for relaxation and recreation.
Read more about Peacock House  ›
Gym
The gym is located next to Asia Spa and is equipped with top-of-the-range kinesis stations, which helps you incorporate both aerobic exercises and muscular strength. Opening hours are 6 am to 10 pm, over 15s only.
Activities
As a guest at Asia Spa, you also gain access to lots of inspirational exercise classes and pleasant activities. Why not try yoga, meditation or pilates? The current timetable is available for you on site.
Useful information for your visit at Asia Spa
Here you will find some useful information for your visit at Asia Spa.
Read our spa information
Opening hours at Asia Spa
Regular opening hours
Monday–Thursday 7 am–9 pm
Friday 7 am–8pm
Saturday–Sunday 8 am–8 pm
The Vitality pool shuts 15 minutes prior to closing time.
Please note that the opening hours may vary during the summer months and on bank holidays. Please contact us on
+46 (0)340-69 01 00
for specific, up-to-date opening hours.
Gym
Our gym is open to our hotel guests and guests at Asia Spa between 6 am and 10 am. Age limit 15 years.
Strictly over 15s only
We have a strict over 15s only rule at Asia Spa, except from during the summer, when children* under 15 are welcome between 8 am–1 pm.
*The child must be potty trained / out of diapers and accompanied by an adult.
