Restaurant
Book a table
Restaurant
When putting together the restaurant menus and creating all the delicious dishes involved, our head chef has been inspired by the four seasons. Our ambition is to serve great food and, wherever possible, use locally produced, seasonal ingredients. The aim is for you to experience something out of the ordinary where food and drink form a beautiful harmony. Our staff will take care of you and are more than happy to provide both service and share their knowledge of wine and ingredients. Welcome to our restaurant in Varberg.
Book a table
HOTEL  AND RESTAURANT WITH AN EXTENSIVE MENU
We offer breakfast, lunch, and à la carte seven days a week. In the evening you can choose beautifully created, individual dishes or complete menus from our
à la carte menu
. Should you prefer to take a seat in the lobby, or on our terrace during the summer months, we have put together a
bistro menu
with a range of nibbles and lighter dishes
Situated on the other side of our hotel building, we also have Japanese restaurant
NAMI
.  Why not incorporate an Asian theme into your entire stay and enjoy a Japanese feast when you next come to visit us?
Our lobby
