RETREAT INCLUDES:
Access to about 30 classes, activities and cold immersions
Accommodation x 2 nights, February 10-12
Breakfastbuffé x 2
Lunch x 3
Dinner x 2
Morning and afternoon tea with snacks
Full access to Asia Spa between classes during your visit.
RETREAT PROGRAM
Friday February 10
From 10.00 morning tea and snacks*
11.00 Classes
12.00 Lunch*
13.00–17.00 Classes
17.30 Opening ceremony
19.00 Dinner*
19.00–22.30 Asia Spa is open for anyone who is keen.
Saturday February 11
07.30 Breakfast
08.30–11.30 Classes and cold immersions according to schedule
10.00 Morning tea and snacks
12.00 Lunch*
13.00–18.30 Classes according to schedule
15.00 Tea and snacks
18.00 Evening meal*
19.00–22.30 Asia Spa is open for anyone who is keen. Japanese menu from Nami served in the Orangery at Asia Spa.
Sunday February 12
07.30 Breakfast
08.30–11.30 Classes and cold immersions according to schedule
10.00 Morning tea and snack
12.00 Lunch*
13.00–14.00 Classes according to schedule
14.45 Closing ceremony
* The meal is served in "Stenhuset".
