How to find us
Welcome to Varberg - the charming coastal town at the heart of Halland, where there is always something going on or something to do. Quite literally on our doorstep, right outside the entrance of our hotel, you will find a whole range of culture, shopping and exciting activities.
Parking information & ticket
As a guest of ours, we can offer parking in all car parks in Varberg (not the car park Kyrkoherden). You park indoors for a fee of SEK 120 SEK/night, in connection with your stay.
Please contact our reception for further information
+46 340 69 01 00
Train & bus
The train station in Varberg is only 500 metres away from the hotel. Book tickets or view train schedules at:
SJ
or
Öresundståg
.
Directions to the hotel
From Gothenburg:
Come off at Varberg North (junction 55) Drive towards the town centre (centrum). At fourth roundabout, drive straight across and follow the signs for Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa after approximately 1000 metres, where you need to turn right. You will find us at Kungsgatan 24–26, right by the market place.
From Malmö:
Come off at Varberg South (junction 53) Drive towards the town centre (centrum). At fourth roundabout, drive straight across and follow the signs for Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa after approximately 1000 metres, where you need to turn right. You will find us at Kungsgatan 24–26, right by the market place.
Centrally located in Varberg
This is where we are located, right by the market place in Varberg, and you can also see the hotel location in relation to the sea and the train station.
Live camera
View from Asia Spa, overlooking Varberg Fortress and the sea.
