All day luxury
Luxurious spa package with treatment
A whole day in the lap of luxury, where you have complete access to our pool, saunas, relaxing lounge and scheduled activity classes at Asia Spa.
This package includes:
Spa lunch - main course, side salad and coffee
A spa kit with yukata (Japanese bathrobe) and slippers to take home with you
A heavenly spa treatment, 60 or 70 minutes long depending on your choice of treatment
