Special offers
/ SUMPTUOUS BREAKFAST
All special offers
Overnight spa package
Day spa
Sumptuous breakfast
A delightfully leisure start to the day
A moment to simply breathe and be, take a break from the hustle and bustle of your everyday life. Breakfast buffet and relaxation at Asia Spa.
This package includes:
Start your day with our ample breakfast buffet, served between 6.30–9.30 am
After which you have 4 hours of pure relaxation at Asia spa with full access to our pool, saunas and relaxation rooms. You can also participate in our scheduled activity classes if you wish.
A spa kit with yukata (Japanese bathrobe), slippers and towel will be provided for you when you arrive at the spa reception (to be handed back at the end of your visit).
Refreshing tea, fruit and water are included during your spa visit.
Read more
From
595 SEK
/adult
Book by email
We will respond to your request within 24 hours. If you have any questions, please contact us at e-mail:
bokning@varbergsstadshotell.com
or phone:
+46 340 69 01 08
Good to know
Age restrictions: strictly over 15s.
This package is available Monday–Friday, (not including Bank Holidays).
Booking information
Close
Booking information
