Boutique room
Book now
Our special offers
Book now
Boutique room
– All round the world in one hotel
All the 66 boutique rooms have their own individual style and furnishings, designed with a modern, yet totally unique flair.  How about sleeping in a crisp Winter Wonderland, an African safari lounge or an urban design metropolis. In this part of our hotel, you will discover innovative approaches and special design features such as circular beds and a bespoke bathtub in the middle of the room.
30 of the double rooms are located on different floors overlooking the roof garden. Available in three different colour schemes: white, beige and purple.
All the rooms are non-smoking rooms. We have naturally included superb facilities, such as:
TV
wifi
modern audiovisual technology
espresso machine
top-of-the-range beds
minibar
shoe shine kits
Many of the rooms also have both a bathtub and shower, and a number of them have a jacuzzi.
Date of arrival
Date of departure
Our special offers
BOOK ONLINE WITH US
When you book a room directly with us, you will also get the best possible deal. Find out more about our price guarantee in the booking terms & conditions below
Booking information
Close
Booking information
PAYMENT
If using the online reservation system for room reservations or spa- & weekend packages, the credit card is for guarantee only. Payment is due at arrival to the Hotel.
If booking a package by phone or email, you will be asked to pay upon arrival. Please advise our staff at the point of booking, if you are planning to use a gift voucher to pay a part or the entire amount.
Day spa packages are to be paid in full when booking online, otherwise at the point of arrival at Asia Spa.
