Conference
CONFERENCE AND KICK-OFF EVENT
To get together and organise a successful conference takes more than just a good conference room. Our winning recipe for successful meetings involves equal parts of traditional town-centre hotel steeped in history, modern facilities, a unique Asian spa and fantastic, service-minded personnel ready to go the extra mile. All these ingredients coupled with our acclaimed restaurant and special atmosphere have made us one of the best hotels with conference facilities on the west coast.
Send a conference inquiry
Contact us
We will be happy to help out with all your arrangements
Please email us on konferens@varbergsstadshotell.com call us on +46 (0)340 69 01 00 and we will be happy to help out with all your arrangements. You can also send a conference inquiry. We will answer to you within 24 hours on weekdays.
Contact us
Meeting & event
