Hotel
/ Deluxe room
Rooms:
Classic room
Boutique room
Deluxe room
(current)
Deluxe room
Book now
OUR SPECIAL OFFERS
Book now
Deluxe room
– Turn-of-the-century design with beautiful, high ceilings
You will find our 28 deluxe rooms in the original part of the hotel, where many of them overlook the town square or Torggatan (Market Street). We have lovingly restored the rooms to their former glory as they would have looked in 1902. Turn-of-the-century romance coupled with classic luxury and the latest mod cons. Gloriously high ceilings and large windows give these room a special airy feel. The rooms are situated lose to
Asia Spa
entrance.
The rooms are all non-smoking and equipped with:
TV
wifi
espresso machine
​
media hub, to which you can connect your own laptop
minibar
hairdryer
ironing board & iron
hypoallergenic pillows and duvets
Date of arrival
Date of departure
OUR SPECIAL OFFERS
BOOK ONLINE WITH US
When you book a room directly with us, you will also get the best possible deal. Find out more about our price guarantee in the booking terms & conditions below.
Booking information
Close
Booking information
PAYMENT
If using the online reservation system for room reservations or spa- & weekend packages, the credit card is for guarantee only. Payment is due at arrival to the Hotel.
If booking a package by phone or email, you will be asked to pay upon arrival. Please advise our staff at the point of booking, if you are planning to use a gift voucher to pay a part or the entire amount.
Day spa packages are to be paid in full when booking online, otherwise at the point of arrival at Asia Spa.
CANCELLATIONS
Room & breakfast bookings: Cancellations are to be done by 2 pm the latest on the day for arrival. Cancellations later than that, or no shows, will be debited in full.
Package bookings: Cancellations are to be done no later than 5 days prior to arrival. Thereafter full repayment will be done if a doctor’s note (medical certificate) is presented. Without valid doctor’s note there will be no repayment.
Day Spa packages: cancellations should be done 48 hrs, prior to arrival at the latest.
The above mentioned clauses are relevant for guests and groups of up to 9 people. Please contact us if you are travelling with a group larger than that. We reserve the right to change our pricing. PLEASE NOTE! For booking of conferences or larger groups other rules apply.
FROM-PRICE WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?
From-price means that the price will vary depending on season as well as which day in the week you arrive. The from-price that is presented in each offer is the lowest available price. If you consult our online booking facility or call our booking department you will be advised of the price that is applicable to the dates you wish to book.
FORCE MAJEURE
Significant restrictions of deliveries or circumstances that are out of the control of the hotel, will entitle us to terminate the contract without obligation to pay damages. (e.g. strike, fire, lockout, natural disaster, war or such like)
Contact
Phone:
+46 340 69 01 80
E-mail:
bokning@varbergsstadshotell.com
Our Deluxe range consists of three different types of rooms
Deluxe premium
Slightly smaller deluxe rooms with a double bed. These rooms are either overlooking Torggatan (Market Street) or facing our peaceful courtyard.
Show more images
1/5
Close
Loading image gallery...
Deluxe superior
Luxurious double rooms in various sizes and different design touches. All of them have beautiful, high ceilings and a light, airy feel and most of them have large windows facing either the town square or Torggatan (Market Street).
Show more images
1/10
Close
Loading image gallery...
Deluxe Royal – Junior suite
Deluxe royal – Junior suite
We have four junior suites with views either across the town square or across the cobbled, pedestrianised shopping area.
A luxurious welcome gift consisting chocolates and champagne awaits your arrival.
Bathtub in the middle of the room.
