Summer in Varberg
Spend your holiday and the summer in the heart of Varberg. Varbergs Stadshotell is located by the square in the town centre and just outside the entrance to our hotel, you will fill find a whole range of cultural experiences and shops. Combine a night at our hotel with a visit to Asia Spa, heading down to the sea for a swim in the salty waves, crab fishing with the kids or surfing at Apelviken.
