Overnight spa package
Day spa
Peace & quiet
Treat yourself to half a day at Asia Spa, where you get to enjoy our pool, saunas, relaxation lounge and scheduled activity classes.
This package includes:
A gorgeous 25-minute spa treatment
Refreshing teas, fruit and water are available in the reception area free of charge to ensure you stay hydrated.
A spa kit with yukata, slippers and towel will be provided for you when you arrive at the spa reception and needs to be handed back at the end of your visit.
PRICES
Monday–Thursday and Friday morning: 890 SEK
Friday afternoon, Saturday–Sunday and all Bank Holidays: 990 SEK
(cannot be booked until 5 days before)
