Kids at Asia Spa
(current)
Kids at Asia Spa
Children also need relaxation – A visit to Asia Spa together with your children is a delightful experience for the whole family. Children need to relax more than you might think and feel it is both exciting and nice to be staying with us.
Kids at Asia Spa
Vitality pool
THE TEMPLE ROOM
Our dark therapy room
OUR LIGHT THERAPY ROOM
THE TEJAS ROOM
Family spa 21 june–22 august 2021
During a few selected weeks in the summer, we open the doors to Asia Spa and welcome the whole family* between 8 am and 1 pm. The rest of the year, only over 15s are allowed into the spa.
*The child should be past the nappy stage and be able to wear normal swimwear, not swim nappies. In our spa treatment area, activity classes and gym, we maintain the over 15s rule even during the summer months.
