Summer week – 7 nights
Summer in Varberg
Stay a bit longer and book our lovely summer package with seven nights, Asia Spa and everything that summer in Varberg has to offer.
This package includes:
Seven overnight stays with our extensive breakfast buffet.
Two half days access to Asia Spa with its array of baths, saunas and activity sessions.
Spa kit, yukata and slippers, to take home after your stay.
For children*, an extra bed and a breakfast buffet is included. Access to Asia Spa in adult company two of the mornings, between 8am–1pm.
*Children are those aged under 15 years.
The child should be past the nappy stage and be able to wear normal swimwear.
Read more
From
3,710 SEK
/adult & 2,870/child
Good to know
Check-in time 3 pm / Check-out time 11 am.
Package is available every day between 19 June–21 August 2022.
