OUR SPECIAL OFFERS
Book now
Classic room
– Traditional and extremely comfortable
Our classic rooms represent a slightly more traditional alternative to the boutique range, boasting very high standard and comfort. They all have beautiful wooden flooring and the latest mod cons. Some of them have been designed with an Asian flair to match the theme of our unique spa. All of the rooms have stylish bathrooms, superbly finished, and the option of either bathtub or shower.
You will find the classic rooms at the centre of the hotel overlooking either the roof garden or the courtyard.
All the rooms are non-smoking rooms and equipped with:
TV
wifi
minibar
hairdryer
kettle
ironing board and iron
hypoallergenic pillows and duvets
Date of arrival
Date of departure
OUR SPECIAL OFFERS
BOOK ONLINE WITH US
When you book a room directly with us, you will also get the best possible deal. Find out more about our price guarantee in the booking terms & conditions below.
