Celebrate your holiday in Varberg
Lovely package with f
our overnight stays, half a day access to
Asia Spa and t
ime to discover the city of Varberg.
This package includes:
Four overnight stays with our extensive breakfast buffet
Half a day (four hours) access to Asia Spa with its array of baths, saunas and activity sessions
Spa kit, yukata and slippers, to take home after your stay
For children*, an extra bed and a breakfast buffet is included. Access to Asia Spa in adult company one of the mornings, between 8am–1pm.
*Children are those aged under 15 years. Only potty trained children are allowed in the spa area.
