Varberg Winter Retreat
From 6,900 SEK
Book
From 6,900 SEK
Book now
Varberg Winter Retreat
Yoga, breathwork and cold therapy with well-known teachers from all over the world on the Swedish west coast.
Date: February 10–12, 2023
Join us for an amazing weekend retreat filled with exciting classes and lectures by world famous teachers and instructors. Indulge in different styles of
yoga
,
breathwork, cold baths, healthy and nourishing food
and full access to our newly expanded
Asia Spa
.
The teachers and space holders that will guide you through the weekend are:
Michael J Wong
,
Kyle Gray
,
Adam Husler
,
Camille Vidal
,
Michelle Baker
,
Lex Reilly
and of course some of our cherised Asia Spa teachers.
Read more
From
6,900 SEK
(1 night from 3,490 SEK)
BOOK THE RETREAT
GOOD TO KNOW
When? February 10-12, 2023.
We also offer one-night packages from SEK 3,490.
Read more about the packages here ›
Classes and lectures will take place in different spaces and lecture halls at Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa, “Stenhuset”, and at the sea. All classes will be held in English.
Strictly over 15s only
WEEKEND INSTRUCTORS
MICHAEL J. WONG WITH FRIENDS
We have had the honour of having Michael J. Wong here on several occasions before. In this unique retreat we have asked him to invite some friends to come along and create another beautiful weekend together with us. More teachers and activities, but still with the same soul – as heartfelt and community based as before. Michael will be holding space for us throughout the weekend, not only during his classes but he is also hosting our very special opening and closing ceremony and has invited the other teachers to be there with him. We can’t wait to be there too.
Read more about the opening and closing ceremony here ›
Michael James Wong
Michael has been teaching yoga and meditation for 15 years and is dedicated to offering a practice with purpose. Michael’s classes are intelligently sequenced with a focus on simple but strong movements that are grounded, clear and precise. All students are welcome no matter their level.
Adam Husler
Adam Husler has taught his unique style of alignment focused, non-dogmatic yoga in over 60 locations across 20 countries, fueled by a fascination with anatomy and a desire to ask ‘why?’.
Adam offers creative, effective and clearly-sequenced teachings that focus on balancing flexibility and strength; physically and mentally.
Kyle Gray
Kyle Gray is an international bestselling author of eight books (including Raise Your Vibration and Angel Numbers) and six oracle decks who is known worldwide for his expertise in angels and spiritual energy.
He is also
a deeply committed practitioner of Kundalini Yoga and Meditation. Kyle is recognised as a senior yoga teacher by the Yoga Alliance Professionals.
Camille Vidal
Cami, known as Mindfully Cami, is a yoga & meditation teacher who focuses on slowing down and creating moments of connection.
She will be joining us to guide you through some Yin Yoga as she invites you to create space in the body and the mind leaving feeling more relaxed and grounded.
Lex Reilly
Lex is no stranger to living in the extreme expression of cold. Having guided 1000’s of participants in nature based experiences, Lex seeks to utilise his ever growing heart chakra to spread his love of nature and human spirit to reignite our wild side.
Lex will be guiding you through your theory and practical elements to the Cold exposure therapy component of your weekend.
Michelle Baker
Michelle Baker is a mentor specializing in personal growth and self-inquiry, a breathwork facilitator, yoga & meditation instructor, and Reiki practitioner & teacher.
Through all of her teachings, she invites you to compassionately navigate your inner knowing, meet your shadows, understand your truth, fortify your body and nourish your spirit – this is her vocation.
Katarina Bergman
Katarina has been practicing yoga for 25 years, and completed her 200 hr yoga teacher training at Gerdahallen in Lund in 2019 where she holds regular Poweryoga and Yinyoga classes.
She has continued her yoga teacher training with Michael James Wong at Krama Yoga School in London and online during the Pandemic. During 2022 she has also completed a Sound Healer training for Holly Husler.
Schedule & classes
See schedule and information about the classes here.
About the classes
The cold bath classes will take place in Varbergs historic fortress and the swimming area connected to it, in the Kattegatt sea.
WELCOME TO VARBERG ON THE SWEDISH WEST COAST
The retreat is held at Varbergs Stadshotell & Asia Spa, in central Varberg. A coastal surf town where you have our famous Varberg's fortress and the Kattegatt sea a short walk from your doorstep. You will also be able to enjoy our Spa, with hot springs and massage pools.
Asia Spa
NEW EXPERIENCES AT ASIA SPA!
During 2022 substantial renovations and extensions of Asia Spa were made. A
new orangery and new rooms for relaxation were created. In December, we open up for even more experiences in the form of an outdoor pool and sauna, with a magical view of the sea and Varberg's fortress.
